title: The Lone Ranger v2 017 (2013) (c2c) (GreenManGroup-DCP).cbr
description: The 'Back East' arc nears its conclusion as the Lone Ranger and Tonto find themselves betrayed, separated and outnumbered. The West's most iconic heroes have crossed the Mississippi looking for answers after being set up by a federal agent. They have found agent Winston Marle. They have also found a new villain who intends to see the Ranger either turn his back on all he stands for or dead and buried. Intrigue and action as the Lone Ranger and Tonto fight to survive in the 'civilized' world.
